title: i CAN'T SEE MY CLUB AS A CLUB OWNER
body:
I CAN'T SEE MY CLUB AS A CLUB OWNER, WHEN I CLICK 'PROFILE' - 'CLUBS', IT SHOWS 'JOIN CLUBS WITH YOUR FRIENDS' AND I CAN'T SEE ANYTHING ABOUT MY ORIGINAL CLUB, SO HOW CAN I DO? 

I ASKED MY FRIEND WHO IN A SAME CLUB, HE TOLD ME I STILL A OWNER IN THIS CLUB.

TAG: ADLCN

replies.body: I had to do a little back-end work, but you should be able to see that club now. Let me know if you're still can't see it!
I'm having the same issue and its been like this for a long time.
